OL,5, A man who lost his job as period       
OL,6, dignity officer is pursuing legal      
OL,7, action against the group that hired    
OL,8, him.                                   
OL,10,FJason Grant is pursuing action under   
OL,11,Fthe Equality Act, with the possibility 
OL,12,Fof a sexual discrimination claim.      
OL,14,FTayside's period dignity working group 
OL,15,Fsaid on Tuesday that it was scrapping  
OL,16,Fthe role following "threats and abuse".
OL,18,FMr Grant's appointment sparked a heated
OL,19,Fdebate online, with critics saying the 
OL,20,Fjob should have gone to a woman.       
